			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've only played a few games so I'm trying to tap into the experiences of those who read this forum to narrow down a search.
<br />

<br />
I'm looking for a MMORPG out there where the game is not so depedent on a single class (i.e. healer).  Is there a game where a few friends of any class can go out and have the same chance to succeed in an encounter as any other group with a different class makeup.  A group of 3 mages has the same chance as a healer, tank and CC.
<br />

<br />
If someone made a game like that it would be awsome.  You can choose the class based on what you enjoy.  Meet new people and play with friends based on how much you enjoy playing together instead of worrying about the class makeup.
<br />

<br />
If someone knows of one I would be very interested in it.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
