		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="99837"></a><b>Sylphan</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Coercer<br /><img src="images/ranks/rank_7.gif" alt="Coercer" title="Coercer" border="0" /><br /><br /><br />Joined: 01 Jan 2004<br />Posts: 247<br /></span><br /></td>
